WEBVTT

1
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:12.074
Watch Online Movies and Series for FREE
www.osdb.link/lm

2
00:00:15.950 --> 00:00:17.890
(Lee Jun Young)

3
00:00:23.030 --> 00:00:25.660
(Lee Ju Myoung)

4
00:00:31.670 --> 00:00:34.340
(Jeon Hye Jin. Jin Goo)

5
00:00:48.950 --> 00:00:51.920
(Reborn Rookie)

6
00:00:56.420 --> 00:00:58.660
What's this? Why are
you coming out of there?

7
00:00:59.390 --> 00:01:00.390
I moved in.

8
00:01:01.030 --> 00:01:02.510
I got kicked out of my home.
thanks to a certain someone.

9
00:01:02.590 --> 00:01:03.760
I get that.

10
00:01:04.130 --> 00:01:06.600
but why did you move here?

11
00:01:07.130 --> 00:01:08.900
Aejeong-dong was the cheapest.

12
00:01:09.370 --> 00:01:12.300
The air is nice. and
the view is to die for.

13
00:01:14.870 --> 00:01:16.510
And there's someone
I'd like to kill here too.

14
00:01:20.280 --> 00:01:21.950
Sweetheart. come and eat.

15
00:01:22.920 --> 00:01:24.350
Okay. Grandma.

16
00:01:25.480 --> 00:01:27.390
Hey. get out of the way.

17
00:01:27.950 --> 00:01:30.360
- What?
- I said. move!

18
00:01:37.000 --> 00:01:38.300
Nice landing.

19
00:01:41.370 --> 00:01:43.270
Let's try to get along.

20
00:01:44.370 --> 00:01:45.600
my dear neighbour.

21
00:01:54.510 --> 00:01:56.620
{\an8}It's been a while. Mr. Hwang.

22
00:02:00.590 --> 00:02:03.080
{\an8}You should let me do
things like this. ma'am.

23
00:02:03.160 --> 00:02:04.920
{\an8}- Seriously.
- Why are you eating at my house?

24
00:02:06.190 --> 00:02:09.060
{\an8}I'm anaemic.

25
00:02:09.360 --> 00:02:11.750
{\an8}and I have malnutrition.
which is rare these days.

26
00:02:11.830 --> 00:02:14.300
{\an8}- I'm all skin and bones.
- Oh. you poor thing.

27
00:02:14.870 --> 00:02:17.540
{\an8}- Look at her.
- Just come and sit.

28
00:02:17.840 --> 00:02:20.470
{\an8}Her mother brought seaweed soup too.

29
00:02:20.770 --> 00:02:22.810
{\an8}- Would you like to try some?
- Oh. yes.

30
00:02:29.050 --> 00:02:30.900
- Goodness.
- Oh. my.

31
00:02:30.980 --> 00:02:32.370
This is salty.

32
00:02:32.450 --> 00:02:34.990
Did you scoop this up from
the sea? Why is it so salty?

33
00:02:35.350 --> 00:02:36.640
- That can't be right.
- Unbelievable.

34
00:02:36.720 --> 00:02:39.190
- Have some water.
- To the chef of Hannam-dong?

35
00:02:39.420 --> 00:02:42.930
No wonder you're so skinny. Goodness.

36
00:02:44.060 --> 00:02:47.830
From now on. you'll eat with us.

37
00:02:48.070 --> 00:02:50.940
This is to pay you back for
the watch. So don't worry. okay?

38
00:02:51.440 --> 00:02:54.270
With inflation these days. we're
adding two more mouths to feed?

39
00:02:54.540 --> 00:02:55.860
An office worker's salary only goes so far.

40
00:02:55.940 --> 00:02:58.610
- Do you think money grows on trees?
- Five hundred dollars a month.

41
00:02:59.140 --> 00:03:00.780
I'll pay you for the meals. ma'am.

42
00:03:00.950 --> 00:03:04.980
Please teach me how to cook too.
I'd be honoured to be your student.

43
00:03:05.680 --> 00:03:07.950
Looks like Grandma's got a side gig.

44
00:03:09.760 --> 00:03:11.160
That's wonderful.

45
00:03:12.060 --> 00:03:13.190
I'm not eating!

46
00:03:13.560 --> 00:03:16.230
- Oh. my.
- Adding two more mouths to feed...

47
00:03:16.530 --> 00:03:19.400
What's with his temper?
Why has he changed so much?

48
00:03:20.170 --> 00:03:22.200
- Thank you for the food.
- Go on. eat up.

49
00:03:22.370 --> 00:03:25.340
- Oh. thank you so much. ma'am.
- Sure.

50
00:03:32.380 --> 00:03:33.380
What are you doing?

51
00:03:33.910 --> 00:03:36.300
Thanks to someone. I had to sell my car.

52
00:03:36.380 --> 00:03:38.050
and now I have to walk everywhere.

53
00:03:38.750 --> 00:03:41.290
A responsible society is
a beautiful thing. isn't it?

54
00:03:42.720 --> 00:03:45.520
What? Are you trying to plant
a bug in my car or something?

55
00:03:46.960 --> 00:03:48.160
What are you talking about?

56
00:03:49.030 --> 00:03:51.260
I know you moved here to dig something up.

57
00:03:51.700 --> 00:03:53.100
but that's not going to work on me.

58
00:03:53.400 --> 00:03:55.570
Don't waste your time.
Move out as soon as you can.

59
00:03:55.830 --> 00:03:57.560
What. are you the landlord or something?

60
00:03:57.640 --> 00:03:58.900
Yes. I bought the place.

61
00:04:00.970 --> 00:04:02.470
- When?
- Just now.

62
00:04:03.380 --> 00:04:04.630
Go check with the real estate agency.

63
00:04:04.710 --> 00:04:05.780
then pack your bags and get out.

64
00:04:08.410 --> 00:04:12.350
Hey. that's an abuse of your power.
We have a lease agreement. you know?

65
00:04:12.680 --> 00:04:13.920
Sue me if you have the money.

66
00:04:14.420 --> 00:04:16.290
You have two weeks
until the end of the month.

67
00:04:17.490 --> 00:04:19.160
- Why that little...
- Oh. right.

68
00:04:19.560 --> 00:04:20.760
If you want to catch the subway. run.

69
00:04:24.330 --> 00:04:25.330
Darn it.

70
00:04:37.010 --> 00:04:40.180
It takes over an hour to
get to work? Seriously...

71
00:04:42.750 --> 00:04:43.850
Good morning!

72
00:04:52.160 --> 00:04:53.190
Or not.

73
00:04:54.930 --> 00:04:57.700
Ms. Kang Bang Geul. you don't
seem to have any sense of urgency.

74
00:04:58.760 --> 00:05:02.470
- And you're the last one to arrive.
- You little...

75
00:05:06.240 --> 00:05:09.440
I'll do better.

76
00:05:12.940 --> 00:05:13.980
Where are you going?

77
00:05:18.150 --> 00:05:21.020
I have to get to my desk
now to clock in on time.

78
00:05:21.550 --> 00:05:23.640
The Materials Team's offer for
returns on defective products.

79
00:05:23.720 --> 00:05:25.890
processing complaints for the
Shipping and Customer Service.

80
00:05:26.020 --> 00:05:27.810
collecting bid notices
from construction firms...

81
00:05:27.890 --> 00:05:29.430
and organising material inventory slips.

82
00:05:29.560 --> 00:05:31.600
There's a long list of
support tasks for other teams.

83
00:05:33.530 --> 00:05:34.830
That's your internal work.

84
00:05:36.570 --> 00:05:39.100
You have separate instructions
from the Future Business Team.

85
00:05:41.010 --> 00:05:43.330
You're a new team that
isn't even fully furnished.

86
00:05:43.410 --> 00:05:44.940
You have instructions already.

87
00:05:45.280 --> 00:05:46.850
Team Leader Hwang Jun Hyeon?

88
00:05:53.950 --> 00:05:58.420
Darn. This is all for
show. I'm not strong at all.

89
00:05:58.620 --> 00:06:02.890
- I've had a bad back for ages.
- No whining.

90
00:06:26.420 --> 00:06:27.790
(Choiseong Logistics)

91
00:06:41.530 --> 00:06:42.600
Go!

92
00:06:45.800 --> 00:06:46.840
All right.

93
00:06:52.410 --> 00:06:53.430
(Hwang Jun Hyeon)

94
00:06:53.510 --> 00:06:55.310
Manage the Jungil-dong construction site.

95
00:06:58.150 --> 00:07:00.410
Hey. put your back into
it. Come on. You hear me?

96
00:07:00.490 --> 00:07:01.720
This is solid rock.

97
00:07:02.020 --> 00:07:04.860
(Choiseong Construction.
Jungil-dong Choiseong Town Site)

98
00:07:06.390 --> 00:07:09.190
Hey. you ever handled a shovel before?

99
00:07:09.590 --> 00:07:11.430
No. this is my first time.

100
00:07:11.700 --> 00:07:15.030
But do you think this is deep
enough to bury a person?

101
00:07:27.550 --> 00:07:30.150
Manage the Choiseong
Solution shareholders' meeting.

102
00:07:33.450 --> 00:07:35.120
Please place them nicely.

103
00:07:38.020 --> 00:07:39.590
- Excuse me. coming through.
- Sure.

104
00:07:40.590 --> 00:07:41.630
Gosh!

105
00:07:44.360 --> 00:07:47.000
- Darn.
- You should've been careful.

106
00:07:48.300 --> 00:07:50.220
Gosh. I spent all day delivering packages.

107
00:07:50.300 --> 00:07:53.200
And the next day. I woke up to
calls from nightmare customers.

108
00:07:53.470 --> 00:07:58.300
After getting an earful. I
just apologised and grovelled.

109
00:07:58.380 --> 00:07:59.640
Then I became a master of the copy machine.

110
00:08:00.610 --> 00:08:02.300
You all know what they call us. right?

111
00:08:02.380 --> 00:08:04.320
The Company-wide Task
Resource Management Team.

112
00:08:04.450 --> 00:08:06.080
Or the "Ex-Con Team" for short.

113
00:08:06.380 --> 00:08:08.240
It makes you feel like you've
committed a crime or something.

114
00:08:08.320 --> 00:08:11.790
My heart pounds whenever I hear a siren.

115
00:08:13.260 --> 00:08:16.630
Why is life so hard? Goodness.

116
00:08:18.500 --> 00:08:20.630
I miss my wife and kids in Canada.

117
00:08:24.500 --> 00:08:25.500
This is hard for you too. isn't it?

118
00:08:26.400 --> 00:08:29.610
I'm sure this change of
environment is tough on Ms. Jo too.

119
00:08:30.180 --> 00:08:32.580
How about you just go back to the US?

120
00:08:33.080 --> 00:08:34.130
I can arrange a place for you there...

121
00:08:34.210 --> 00:08:37.580
No. It's not hard at all.

122
00:08:40.220 --> 00:08:41.220
Oh. honestly.

123
00:08:52.900 --> 00:08:53.930
What? What is it now?

124
00:08:58.400 --> 00:08:59.440
Look.

125
00:08:59.670 --> 00:09:01.670
Support work for the
Financial Business Division.

126
00:09:02.040 --> 00:09:05.210
Just thinking about that jerk
gives me a surge of energy.

127
00:09:15.790 --> 00:09:18.090
(Credit Union)

128
00:09:20.090 --> 00:09:22.490
- How can I help you?
- I'd like to withdraw some money.

129
00:09:35.210 --> 00:09:38.240
This lip tint is a bestseller at Sephora.

130
00:09:38.680 --> 00:09:40.480
Number six. Mauve Cherry.

131
00:09:40.650 --> 00:09:42.780
Buy it. and with a quick swipe.

132
00:09:43.050 --> 00:09:44.420
you'll earn cashback right away.

133
00:09:45.780 --> 00:09:49.410
If you use this debit card. you earn
cashback every time you buy coffee.

134
00:09:49.490 --> 00:09:51.420
Can I help you apply for one?

135
00:09:59.760 --> 00:10:02.370
Bang Geul will never give up.

136
00:10:02.830 --> 00:10:06.640
Stop with the nonsense and
pressure her more to quit immediately.

137
00:10:07.840 --> 00:10:10.140
And keep Kang Jae Gyeong away from her.

138
00:10:11.480 --> 00:10:13.470
This will just make things worse
between the father and daughter.

139
00:10:13.550 --> 00:10:14.670
She looks ready to tear him apart...

140
00:10:14.750 --> 00:10:16.180
whenever she hears Hwang Jun Hyeon's name.

141
00:10:17.450 --> 00:10:20.720
Any new developments
with Professor Min Seok Do?

142
00:10:22.350 --> 00:10:23.560
He resigned.

143
00:10:24.620 --> 00:10:26.590
And there are rumours he'll
be joining Choiseong Group.

144
00:10:26.720 --> 00:10:29.130
He might as well be advertising
that he's an accomplice.

145
00:10:31.900 --> 00:10:32.930
Who are you?

146
00:10:34.530 --> 00:10:37.170
Use this video to get some
leverage on Kang Jae Gyeong.

147
00:10:37.870 --> 00:10:39.840
She was the last person to
visit the hospital room that day.

148
00:10:40.000 --> 00:10:41.770
It's not proof that she killed me.

149
00:10:42.410 --> 00:10:43.510
This isn't enough.

150
00:10:44.610 --> 00:10:45.610
What about what I asked you to check?

151
00:10:47.680 --> 00:10:50.620
They said the CCTV stopped
recording due to a security check.

152
00:10:51.150 --> 00:10:53.890
but the person in charge supposedly
mixed up the inspection date.

153
00:10:54.320 --> 00:10:56.120
The hospital didn't
make a big deal out of it.

154
00:10:56.690 --> 00:10:59.360
Jae Gyeong must have pulled
some strings so they wouldn't.

155
00:11:00.230 --> 00:11:01.730
Where is this guy now?

156
00:11:01.830 --> 00:11:02.830
(Personnel Record Card: Ham Du Ho)

157
00:11:07.300 --> 00:11:08.330
Good.

158
00:11:08.670 --> 00:11:10.970
I have no clue.

159
00:11:17.410 --> 00:11:19.680
He's been on sick leave and
hasn't come to work for days.

160
00:11:20.250 --> 00:11:22.350
He asks for a fortune. then disappears.

161
00:11:23.110 --> 00:11:25.680
Find him fast. Before
this gets out of hand.

162
00:11:25.950 --> 00:11:29.890
Yes. We're looking into his
home. family. and all his contacts.

163
00:11:35.030 --> 00:11:37.030
(Chairwoman Kang Jae Gyeong)

164
00:11:38.030 --> 00:11:41.530
I hear the department heads are
complaining about being overworked.

165
00:11:41.730 --> 00:11:43.430
Aren't you working them a little
too hard. Team Leader Hwang?

166
00:11:43.640 --> 00:11:46.300
Results are most crucial
right after taking office.

167
00:11:46.700 --> 00:11:48.060
Everyone needs to be on their toes.

168
00:11:48.140 --> 00:11:49.130
(Chairwoman Kang Jae Gyeong)

169
00:11:49.210 --> 00:11:51.980
Also. we heard from Taeha.

170
00:11:52.810 --> 00:11:54.070
They want the Daesan
Hydrogen Complex deal...

171
00:11:54.150 --> 00:11:55.150
wrapped up by next week.

172
00:11:56.610 --> 00:11:58.520
So they just want to take what's theirs?

173
00:12:00.220 --> 00:12:01.550
Secretary Yeo. you can handle that.

174
00:12:02.390 --> 00:12:03.690
(Chairman Kang Jae Gyeong)

175
00:12:03.790 --> 00:12:05.320
Don't you worry about
it. Team Leader Hwang.

176
00:12:05.820 --> 00:12:06.890
Yes. Chairwoman.

177
00:12:13.430 --> 00:12:14.630
(Chairwoman Kang Jae Gyeong)

178
00:12:15.730 --> 00:12:17.060
(Personnel Record Card: Ham Du Ho)

179
00:12:17.140 --> 00:12:18.170
(Chairwoman Kang Jae Gyeong)

180
00:12:22.440 --> 00:12:24.040
(Lee Sang Jae)

181
00:12:26.140 --> 00:12:28.580
I think Kang Jae Gyeong is
trying to get to the security guard.

182
00:12:29.080 --> 00:12:31.280
- We have to get to him first...
- I've found him. Chairman.

183
00:12:32.420 --> 00:12:34.690
Do you trust Hwang Jun Hyeon?

184
00:12:36.750 --> 00:12:38.120
Trust him?

185
00:12:39.260 --> 00:12:41.030
He only does things to
stay in my good graces.

186
00:12:42.030 --> 00:12:44.400
Kang Bang Geul moved in next door to me.

187
00:12:44.830 --> 00:12:46.350
I think she's trying to find something out.

188
00:12:46.430 --> 00:12:47.430
What do you want me to do?

189
00:12:47.600 --> 00:12:50.070
I told you I was leaving
the two of them to you.

190
00:12:51.170 --> 00:12:52.240
Handle it.

191
00:12:52.740 --> 00:12:54.340
As I promised. I'll make sure...

192
00:12:55.870 --> 00:12:58.040
the two of them are sent to
the US by the end of the month.

193
00:12:59.980 --> 00:13:01.050
More importantly.

194
00:13:03.350 --> 00:13:06.120
what's making that old man so confident?

195
00:13:15.860 --> 00:13:17.060
Give Taeha a message.

196
00:13:18.560 --> 00:13:21.230
If they don't deliver the money
and shares by the end of the week.

197
00:13:22.700 --> 00:13:26.440
they'll never get their hands on
our core hydrogen technology.

198
00:13:32.210 --> 00:13:33.240
Please.

199
00:13:34.610 --> 00:13:35.750
Darn it.

200
00:13:42.820 --> 00:13:44.390
(Financial Backer)

201
00:13:44.690 --> 00:13:46.820
You have to light a fire under
them before they open their wallets.

202
00:13:47.430 --> 00:13:48.690
(Financial Backer)

203
00:13:49.690 --> 00:13:50.760
Secretary Yeo?

204
00:14:06.610 --> 00:14:09.850
- Darn it!
- Oh. dear.

205
00:14:10.550 --> 00:14:11.820
I'm so sorry.

206
00:14:11.950 --> 00:14:13.790
Do you think saying sorry fixes everything?

207
00:14:14.050 --> 00:14:15.090
I'm sorry.

208
00:14:15.650 --> 00:14:16.750
Unbelievable.

209
00:14:17.420 --> 00:14:20.760
Let me pay for your dry cleaning
and medical bills. Oh. what a mess.

210
00:14:21.630 --> 00:14:24.400
What. you think money can solve everything?

211
00:14:26.500 --> 00:14:28.430
Plus extra for your trouble.

212
00:14:30.470 --> 00:14:32.990
Excuse me! One bowl of ramyeon over here.

213
00:14:33.070 --> 00:14:34.530
and could you please clean this up?

214
00:14:34.610 --> 00:14:36.910
- Thanks.
- My apologies.

215
00:14:37.580 --> 00:14:38.610
Well. then.

216
00:14:42.180 --> 00:14:43.310
Eight. seven.

217
00:14:44.350 --> 00:14:46.280
one. zero. one. two.

218
00:14:48.120 --> 00:14:49.350
(Personnel Record Card)

219
00:14:56.460 --> 00:14:58.060
(Financial Backer)

220
00:15:01.830 --> 00:15:03.050
(Compose New Message)

221
00:15:03.130 --> 00:15:04.140
(Financial Backer)

222
00:15:04.540 --> 00:15:05.570
At 10pm.

223
00:15:06.240 --> 00:15:07.570
The parking lot under Sehwa Bridge.

224
00:15:08.270 --> 00:15:09.270
I want 500.000 dollars.

225
00:15:12.810 --> 00:15:13.980
(Okay)

226
00:15:30.260 --> 00:15:31.330
What's the status?

227
00:15:31.500 --> 00:15:33.500
We've agreed to pay him what he asked for.

228
00:15:33.770 --> 00:15:34.900
so we should wait a little longer.

229
00:15:37.070 --> 00:15:38.470
Still nothing from Taeha?

230
00:15:38.870 --> 00:15:41.810
It seems like they're
intentionally avoiding my calls.

231
00:15:42.210 --> 00:15:43.980
And Secretary Jo is
ignoring my calls altogether.

232
00:15:50.280 --> 00:15:52.280
I wonder what Chairman Na is banking on.

233
00:15:53.820 --> 00:15:55.090
It couldn't be that. could it?

234
00:16:20.680 --> 00:16:21.850
What's he doing here?

235
00:16:26.420 --> 00:16:28.220
(Financial Backer)

236
00:16:33.090 --> 00:16:35.160
Na Byeong Mo. that scum.

237
00:16:43.940 --> 00:16:45.970
- Anyone here?
- No one. sir.

238
00:16:46.370 --> 00:16:48.240
- Head to his house.
- Yes. sir.

239
00:16:58.220 --> 00:17:00.420
(Personnel Record Card. Address)

240
00:17:19.100 --> 00:17:20.740
The security guard disappeared?

241
00:17:21.070 --> 00:17:22.270
We were one step behind.

242
00:17:22.870 --> 00:17:25.710
The place was a mess. Nothing to be found.

243
00:17:26.810 --> 00:17:29.410
How could she team up with
someone like Na Byeong Mo?

244
00:17:30.410 --> 00:17:33.150
She knew full well how much you. hated him.

245
00:17:34.550 --> 00:17:35.590
No.

246
00:17:36.590 --> 00:17:38.360
No matter how I look
at it. this doesn't add up.

247
00:17:39.620 --> 00:17:41.680
Jae Gyeong has no reason
to involve Na Byeong Mo...

248
00:17:41.760 --> 00:17:43.330
in something that could
be used against her.

249
00:17:44.100 --> 00:17:45.100
Then...

250
00:17:48.330 --> 00:17:50.940
Chairman Na is trying to
blackmail Kang Jae Gyeong?

251
00:17:51.870 --> 00:17:53.340
Na Byeong Mo knows.

252
00:17:53.940 --> 00:17:55.540
That Jae Gyeong was the one who killed me.

253
00:17:57.110 --> 00:17:59.640
He was trying to get the CCTV
footage from the security guard.

254
00:17:59.810 --> 00:18:01.780
If Chairman Na gets his hands on it.

255
00:18:02.310 --> 00:18:04.120
he'll obviously use it to
make a deal for Choiseong.

256
00:18:05.020 --> 00:18:06.940
In that case. wouldn't it be better...

257
00:18:07.020 --> 00:18:09.840
if Kang Jae Gyeong's
people got the security guard?

258
00:18:09.920 --> 00:18:12.620
So it's fine for Jae Gyeong to
destroy the evidence of her crime?

259
00:18:16.030 --> 00:18:17.360
There's only one thing left to do.

260
00:18:20.570 --> 00:18:22.320
We have to hope this
has the proof we need...

261
00:18:22.400 --> 00:18:23.670
to prove that Jae Gyeong is the culprit.

262
00:18:24.540 --> 00:18:25.690
(Suspicious Death of Former
Chairman Kang Yong Ho)

263
00:18:25.770 --> 00:18:26.770
(Anonymous Tip)

264
00:18:29.870 --> 00:18:31.780
Hayoung Daily received a tip.

265
00:18:34.280 --> 00:18:35.630
I've stopped them from running the story.

266
00:18:35.710 --> 00:18:37.110
(Kang Yong Ho Died After
Kang Jae Gyeong's Visit)

267
00:18:39.750 --> 00:18:41.090
A tip?

268
00:18:41.450 --> 00:18:43.920
That means we're not the only
ones who suspect Kang Jae Gyeong.

269
00:18:44.660 --> 00:18:46.410
It also means there's
hospital CCTV footage...

270
00:18:46.490 --> 00:18:47.730
from the day of Father's accident.

271
00:18:48.860 --> 00:18:50.730
Proof that Kang Jae
Gyeong is the real killer.

272
00:18:51.400 --> 00:18:53.620
What about the source? Isn't the
paper's president your best friend?

273
00:18:53.700 --> 00:18:55.370
He said he doesn't know.
It was an anonymous tip.

274
00:18:55.630 --> 00:18:58.540
I feel like he's hiding something. though.

275
00:19:00.200 --> 00:19:01.510
You're here. Madam Chairwoman!

276
00:19:03.570 --> 00:19:04.580
(Choiseong C&T. President's Office)

277
00:19:06.740 --> 00:19:09.400
You should have called me.
I'm surprised the Chairwoman...

278
00:19:09.480 --> 00:19:11.120
would trouble herself to come all this way.

279
00:19:13.720 --> 00:19:14.790
You.

280
00:19:16.820 --> 00:19:18.620
Did you meet with the
president of Hayoung Daily?

281
00:19:19.220 --> 00:19:20.560
Hayoung Daily...

282
00:19:21.930 --> 00:19:22.960
You mean Jeong Hak Hui?

283
00:19:23.260 --> 00:19:25.880
I haven't talked to him in a while. Why?

284
00:19:25.960 --> 00:19:27.200
Don't play dumb.

285
00:19:28.170 --> 00:19:29.670
Everyone knows you two are best friends.

286
00:19:31.770 --> 00:19:33.070
Did he say anything to you?

287
00:19:34.840 --> 00:19:37.310
About what? Did an article get published?

288
00:19:39.010 --> 00:19:40.110
Don't tell me...

289
00:19:41.480 --> 00:19:44.820
If you're plotting something with
Kang Bang Geul behind my back.

290
00:19:47.050 --> 00:19:48.590
you'll have to give up your position.

291
00:20:02.870 --> 00:20:06.300
Don't jinx yourself by saying her
name. You have big things to do.

292
00:20:28.390 --> 00:20:29.730
You're getting a call.

293
00:20:30.230 --> 00:20:32.800
Answer it. It seems important.

294
00:20:50.280 --> 00:20:51.570
I was looking for you.
You weren't in your office.

295
00:20:51.650 --> 00:20:54.120
- About Daesan Hydrogen Complex...
- We'll talk later. Mr. Hwang.

296
00:21:00.320 --> 00:21:03.060
I guess they don't let the
traitor in on the important stuff.

297
00:21:07.500 --> 00:21:10.000
She took a call and stormed
out with a foul look on her face.

298
00:21:11.500 --> 00:21:13.870
- Was it about the tip?
- What tip?

299
00:21:14.770 --> 00:21:17.260
I thought you were Kang
Jae Gyeong's favourite.

300
00:21:17.340 --> 00:21:18.710
but you're totally out of the loop.

301
00:21:18.980 --> 00:21:20.810
Tell me what you're talking about.

302
00:21:21.010 --> 00:21:22.970
A newspaper got a tip
that Kang Jae Gyeong...

303
00:21:23.050 --> 00:21:24.550
is the one who killed my dad.

304
00:21:25.520 --> 00:21:27.410
Kang Jae Gyeong's face
was caught clear as day...

305
00:21:27.490 --> 00:21:29.450
on the hospital CCTV that
was supposedly broken.

306
00:21:31.390 --> 00:21:33.190
See? You can't get away with murder.

307
00:21:33.890 --> 00:21:37.430
- The truth always comes out.
- It was Hayoung Daily. wasn't it?

308
00:21:38.630 --> 00:21:40.230
Did you see the article
through Kang Jae Seong?

309
00:21:40.660 --> 00:21:42.400
What exactly was on the CCTV footage?

310
00:21:43.170 --> 00:21:44.520
What picture of Kang Jae Gyeong?

311
00:21:44.600 --> 00:21:46.070
You're not asking the
most important question.

312
00:21:46.800 --> 00:21:49.670
You must know who the informant is.

313
00:21:51.410 --> 00:21:54.110
The proof that Kang Jae
Gyeong killed my dad...

314
00:21:55.550 --> 00:21:57.050
The informant has it. right?

315
00:21:58.820 --> 00:21:59.820
Hey.

316
00:22:01.090 --> 00:22:03.920
Stop running around
playing amateur detective.

317
00:22:05.290 --> 00:22:07.590
There's nothing you can do.

318
00:22:12.500 --> 00:22:13.830
Why that little...

319
00:22:14.500 --> 00:22:15.630
Jae Seong.

320
00:22:16.730 --> 00:22:18.940
It looks like Hwang Jun Hyeon
knows who the informant is. right?

321
00:22:19.640 --> 00:22:21.070
Do you think it's someone we know?

322
00:22:25.780 --> 00:22:28.170
(Choiseong C&T. President's Office)

323
00:22:28.250 --> 00:22:30.210
(Entrance)

324
00:22:54.710 --> 00:22:57.510
Look at this one. It's packed with roe.

325
00:22:58.880 --> 00:23:00.780
It's a delicacy when you eat it whole.

326
00:23:02.050 --> 00:23:03.530
You said you had something to say.

327
00:23:03.610 --> 00:23:05.520
You're always in such a hurry.

328
00:23:10.450 --> 00:23:11.720
(Daesan Hydrogen Complex
and Tech Transfer Agreement)

329
00:23:13.290 --> 00:23:15.030
(Daesan Hydrogen Complex
and Tech Transfer Agreement)

330
00:23:16.730 --> 00:23:19.060
The core technology of the
Daesan Hydrogen Complex.

331
00:23:19.730 --> 00:23:22.870
You'll transfer it without
the final payment. Sign it.

332
00:23:28.070 --> 00:23:29.940
(Daesan Hydrogen Complex
and Tech Transfer Agreement)

333
00:23:31.580 --> 00:23:33.380
I never agreed to a contract like this.

334
00:23:35.480 --> 00:23:37.620
Or will you wash your hands
of Choiseong altogether?

335
00:23:37.880 --> 00:23:41.010
- And I'll graciously let you go.
- Chairman Na!

336
00:23:41.090 --> 00:23:42.370
How dare you raise your voice at me?

337
00:23:42.450 --> 00:23:44.490
You're worse than an animal
for killing your own father.

338
00:23:54.030 --> 00:23:56.820
Place an ad for Taeha
Energy in the Hayoung Daily.

339
00:23:56.900 --> 00:23:59.040
President Jeong does a fine job.

340
00:24:00.200 --> 00:24:01.240
Yes. Chairman.

341
00:24:02.910 --> 00:24:04.010
Was it you?

342
00:24:04.940 --> 00:24:08.910
- You framed me as the killer?
- Frame you? Isn't that the truth?

343
00:24:11.350 --> 00:24:13.480
I should've never gotten
involved with scum like you.

344
00:24:16.350 --> 00:24:17.550
At first.

345
00:24:18.460 --> 00:24:20.420
she was going to drug
Father with the sleeping pills...

346
00:24:20.860 --> 00:24:23.460
she got from Professor Min
so Father wouldn't wake up.

347
00:24:24.360 --> 00:24:26.260
But then Father's eyes suddenly shot open.

348
00:24:26.700 --> 00:24:27.800
so she just grabbed the pillow...

349
00:24:28.830 --> 00:24:31.600
and just smothered him.

350
00:24:32.740 --> 00:24:34.610
So. did he say he did
everything I told him to?

351
00:24:35.570 --> 00:24:36.570
Or...

352
00:24:37.310 --> 00:24:38.880
that he only pretended to go along with it?

353
00:24:39.580 --> 00:24:41.480
Your husband is my accomplice.

354
00:24:42.310 --> 00:24:44.550
You want to see whose crime is worse?

355
00:24:53.690 --> 00:24:55.460
A recording like that
won't hold up as evidence.

356
00:24:56.330 --> 00:24:57.960
Do you really think
people will believe that?

357
00:24:58.160 --> 00:25:00.380
You cremated your father
as if you couldn't wait.

358
00:25:00.460 --> 00:25:02.900
manipulated the board. and
took over as Chairwoman.

359
00:25:03.470 --> 00:25:05.390
Even your family suspects you.

360
00:25:05.470 --> 00:25:07.190
Do you think the public
will believe your side?

361
00:25:07.270 --> 00:25:08.340
Don't slander me.

362
00:25:09.340 --> 00:25:12.210
My father was definitely alive when I left.

363
00:25:15.910 --> 00:25:17.110
Who are you?

364
00:25:22.190 --> 00:25:23.190
Seriously.

365
00:25:24.920 --> 00:25:26.590
You seem to have nine lives.

366
00:25:34.400 --> 00:25:37.170
It wasn't me. I didn't kill him.

367
00:25:38.640 --> 00:25:39.640
Don't tell me...

368
00:25:41.510 --> 00:25:43.170
Did you kill my father?

369
00:25:43.340 --> 00:25:47.540
You didn't care if your father
dropped dead or was murdered.

370
00:25:48.110 --> 00:25:50.310
but you finally look curious now.

371
00:25:53.220 --> 00:25:54.280
Kang Yong Ho...

372
00:25:55.220 --> 00:25:56.910
was murdered by his own
daughter blinded by greed...

373
00:25:56.990 --> 00:25:57.990
for the chairman's seat

374
00:25:58.720 --> 00:26:00.720
I'm going to make that the truth.

375
00:26:02.130 --> 00:26:03.360
What are you. the Almighty?

376
00:26:04.600 --> 00:26:08.530
- How will you hide the truth?
- You can't just hide the truth!

377
00:26:12.000 --> 00:26:13.400
You have to eliminate it.

378
00:26:23.950 --> 00:26:25.920
I heard that guy contacted you too.

379
00:26:26.550 --> 00:26:29.350
He said he'd tell you what really
happened that day for a hefty price.

380
00:26:34.190 --> 00:26:36.590
He shouldn't have pushed his luck.

381
00:27:01.250 --> 00:27:05.120
(Eunpo Sashimi House)

382
00:27:36.890 --> 00:27:39.990
(Kang Jae Gyeong)

383
00:27:42.860 --> 00:27:46.130
(Kang Jae Gyeong)

384
00:27:48.830 --> 00:27:49.970
Yes. ma'am.

385
00:27:52.200 --> 00:27:53.200
Where are you?

386
00:28:05.650 --> 00:28:08.020
(The Late Kang Yong Ho)

387
00:28:16.760 --> 00:28:18.760
Are you hiding something from me?

388
00:28:23.430 --> 00:28:25.870
I came here after reading
the tip sent by Secretary Yeo.

389
00:28:27.070 --> 00:28:28.070
Is it really true?

390
00:28:29.770 --> 00:28:31.510
Did you kill him?

391
00:28:33.380 --> 00:28:34.710
Don't be so cocky.

392
00:28:37.750 --> 00:28:38.880
Did you kill him?

393
00:28:40.720 --> 00:28:42.720
- Your father.
- I said. shut it!

394
00:28:55.430 --> 00:28:57.500
If that's a weakness.
we need to prepare for it.

395
00:28:59.240 --> 00:29:00.240
Answer me.

396
00:29:04.910 --> 00:29:06.180
It was Na Byeong Mo.

397
00:29:07.180 --> 00:29:08.750
He's trying to frame me for it.

398
00:29:10.410 --> 00:29:12.450
I got completely taken in by Chairman Na.

399
00:29:13.550 --> 00:29:15.050
Chairman Na killed him?

400
00:29:17.020 --> 00:29:18.060
Are you sure?

401
00:29:21.830 --> 00:29:24.260
Unbelievable. The whole world suspects me.

402
00:29:25.400 --> 00:29:26.500
Why would I kill my own father?

403
00:29:26.960 --> 00:29:28.200
He was going to die soon anyway.

404
00:29:29.270 --> 00:29:31.340
I already had Choiseong
in my grasp. Why would I?

405
00:29:31.470 --> 00:29:33.770
So you're truly innocent. right?

406
00:29:35.110 --> 00:29:37.470
I am. Not in the slightest.

407
00:29:38.840 --> 00:29:40.780
Then you should request a
police investigation right now.

408
00:29:41.450 --> 00:29:42.450
No.

409
00:29:45.020 --> 00:29:46.950
If this blows up. I'll
be at a disadvantage.

410
00:29:49.520 --> 00:29:50.710
We just need to find proof...

411
00:29:50.790 --> 00:29:52.160
that Chairman Na is the killer.

412
00:29:54.560 --> 00:29:56.060
and then we can instantly
turn the tables on him.

413
00:29:57.830 --> 00:29:59.580
I'll drag Na Byeong Mo to the gutter...

414
00:29:59.660 --> 00:30:01.770
and repay today's humiliation tenfold.

415
00:30:02.000 --> 00:30:03.800
I have to protect Choiseong
and get my revenge.

416
00:30:04.640 --> 00:30:06.640
Isn't that the only way for
my father to rest in peace?

417
00:30:09.710 --> 00:30:11.980
Is that really what your
father would've wanted?

418
00:30:13.480 --> 00:30:14.680
Then what would he have wanted?

419
00:30:17.250 --> 00:30:19.320
If he'd just passed quietly.
none of this would've happened.

420
00:30:20.550 --> 00:30:22.090
So selfish. right to the end.

421
00:30:23.790 --> 00:30:25.360
I'm trying to avenge
him and give him peace.

422
00:30:26.290 --> 00:30:27.320
so what's the problem?

423
00:30:32.330 --> 00:30:34.000
Should I be the one to find it for you?

424
00:30:35.770 --> 00:30:37.830
The evidence that Na
Byeong Mo killed your father.

425
00:30:39.300 --> 00:30:41.570
He already destroyed the
hospital's CCTV footage.

426
00:30:42.510 --> 00:30:43.730
He killed the witness too.

427
00:30:43.810 --> 00:30:45.110
If there's no evidence.
then we'll create it.

428
00:30:46.880 --> 00:30:47.910
I told you.

429
00:30:50.210 --> 00:30:51.880
I'm with you all the way.

430
00:30:54.920 --> 00:30:57.250
What happened between
you and Na Byeong Mo...

431
00:31:00.220 --> 00:31:02.160
Tell me everything.

432
00:31:40.830 --> 00:31:42.620
- You're here. Father.
- Yes.

433
00:31:42.700 --> 00:31:44.700
- This way.
- Okay.

434
00:31:55.050 --> 00:31:56.550
Why is Chairman Na here?

435
00:32:00.020 --> 00:32:01.750
(Chairwoman Kang Jae Gyeong)

436
00:32:13.160 --> 00:32:16.330
The light in here is amazing. It
makes you want it for yourself.

437
00:32:16.470 --> 00:32:19.900
(Chairwoman Kang Jae Gyeong)

438
00:32:21.710 --> 00:32:24.170
You still have to sign the
Daesan Hydrogen Complex deal.

439
00:32:25.280 --> 00:32:26.280
Final payment of 100 million dollars.

440
00:32:27.740 --> 00:32:29.580
Settle it according to
the contract. Chairman.

441
00:32:31.480 --> 00:32:34.480
Please. I ask of you.

442
00:32:38.690 --> 00:32:41.930
Should I have played the
recording at the executive meeting?

443
00:32:42.990 --> 00:32:45.500
A lot of people there
still miss Kang Yong Ho.

444
00:32:47.600 --> 00:32:49.200
I'm just kidding.

445
00:32:51.700 --> 00:32:52.700
But...

446
00:32:53.570 --> 00:32:56.110
it wasn't easy for me to get here either.

447
00:32:56.870 --> 00:32:58.380
And I took some major losses along the way.

448
00:33:00.410 --> 00:33:01.980
You'll have to compensate.

449
00:33:02.280 --> 00:33:04.680
You have that secret
stash of money. don't you?

450
00:33:05.850 --> 00:33:07.620
Siren Capital Partners. I believe?

451
00:33:09.720 --> 00:33:11.920
While I'm here. I suppose I'll
have a look around Choiseong.

452
00:33:12.360 --> 00:33:14.090
Don't mind me.

453
00:33:15.430 --> 00:33:16.760
Just carry on with your work.

454
00:33:47.860 --> 00:33:49.160
(Chairwoman Kang Jae Gyeong)

455
00:33:49.730 --> 00:33:50.880
I've invited you all here today...

456
00:33:50.960 --> 00:33:52.700
as it's a good chance
for us to get acquainted.

457
00:33:53.330 --> 00:33:54.660
In our future with Taeha Group.

458
00:33:55.100 --> 00:33:57.030
there will be many more
projects we can do together.

459
00:33:58.440 --> 00:33:59.740
You'll give them the wrong idea.

460
00:33:59.900 --> 00:34:01.160
(Chairwoman Kang Jae Gyeong)

461
00:34:01.240 --> 00:34:02.940
I'm the one helping.

462
00:34:03.740 --> 00:34:08.040
Having the title of chairwoman
doesn't solve everything. does it?

463
00:34:08.650 --> 00:34:10.150
And Choiseong has no adults.

464
00:34:13.420 --> 00:34:14.420
President Hyeon.

465
00:34:14.850 --> 00:34:17.190
The automated logistics and
distribution system at Choiseong...

466
00:34:17.920 --> 00:34:19.560
I hear it's running quite well.

467
00:34:19.720 --> 00:34:20.780
(Hyeon Jin. President of Choiseong Distribution)

468
00:34:20.860 --> 00:34:23.260
We're thinking of expanding
into that area as well.

469
00:34:23.990 --> 00:34:25.760
It'd be even better if we did it together.

470
00:34:28.400 --> 00:34:32.100
Are you already in discussions
with Chairwoman Kang Jae Gyeong?

471
00:34:34.440 --> 00:34:37.410
Why don't we discuss it over a meal?

472
00:34:38.010 --> 00:34:39.380
Taeha will be hosting today.

473
00:34:43.680 --> 00:34:44.680
Chairman Na and his daughter...

474
00:34:45.550 --> 00:34:47.350
even held a luncheon with
the company presidents.

475
00:34:48.820 --> 00:34:50.850
Looks like Na Eun Se is
having the time of her life.

476
00:34:52.220 --> 00:34:53.920
(Daesan Hydrogen Complex
and Tech Transfer Agreement)

477
00:34:56.890 --> 00:34:58.500
If I provoke him without cause.

478
00:34:59.160 --> 00:35:00.860
he might leak the footage
from the hospital room.

479
00:35:02.170 --> 00:35:03.730
Try not to worry so much.

480
00:35:05.400 --> 00:35:08.310
Leverage is only powerful
as long as you hold on to it.

481
00:35:09.070 --> 00:35:10.060
What?

482
00:35:10.140 --> 00:35:12.610
I'm saying Na Byeong Mo
won't play his card just yet.

483
00:35:13.780 --> 00:35:14.780
So.

484
00:35:15.980 --> 00:35:17.280
whatever happens. hold your ground.

485
00:35:18.820 --> 00:35:20.400
It's better than stepping down.

486
00:35:20.480 --> 00:35:21.750
not after all you did to get that position.

487
00:35:21.920 --> 00:35:22.910
Hwang Jun Hyeon.

488
00:35:22.990 --> 00:35:24.810
If you hand over the core
technology without the final payment.

489
00:35:24.890 --> 00:35:26.320
do you think the
shareholders will just stand by?

490
00:35:26.820 --> 00:35:28.210
A chairwoman who gets pushed around...

491
00:35:28.290 --> 00:35:29.830
on her first deal since taking over.

492
00:35:30.260 --> 00:35:32.100
What will the employees think of that?

493
00:35:33.260 --> 00:35:35.900
This directly reflects on your
capabilities as the Chairwoman.

494
00:35:36.700 --> 00:35:39.340
Stop lecturing me and give me a solution.

495
00:35:40.000 --> 00:35:41.000
So what's your plan?

496
00:35:41.200 --> 00:35:43.330
Chairman Na is blackmailing
you with rumours...

497
00:35:43.410 --> 00:35:45.300
and stole the hydrogen technology
without making the final payment.

498
00:35:45.380 --> 00:35:47.580
Isn't that enough to throw a jab?

499
00:35:49.480 --> 00:35:51.850
How do you expect to
manipulate a snake like him?

500
00:35:53.780 --> 00:35:54.950
You have me. don't you?

501
00:35:55.820 --> 00:35:56.820
The icon of betrayal.

502
00:35:59.360 --> 00:36:01.310
You think Chairman Na will trust you?

503
00:36:01.390 --> 00:36:02.660
He either trusts me. or he's dead.

504
00:36:03.890 --> 00:36:05.000
It'll be one or the other.

505
00:36:06.160 --> 00:36:08.470
You won't lose anything either way.

506
00:36:16.910 --> 00:36:17.910
Secretary Yeo.

507
00:36:18.780 --> 00:36:21.010
From now on. follow Team
Leader Hwang's orders.

508
00:36:22.180 --> 00:36:23.850
Give him whatever support he needs.

509
00:36:26.920 --> 00:36:29.520
I'm betting everything on
you. Hwang Jun Hyeon.

510
00:36:40.300 --> 00:36:41.360
Chairman Na Byeong Mo.

511
00:36:43.530 --> 00:36:44.920
This is Hwang Jun Hyeon
from Future Business Team...

512
00:36:45.000 --> 00:36:46.040
at Choiseong Group.

513
00:36:46.840 --> 00:36:47.820
(Friday. March 20. 11:54am)

514
00:36:47.900 --> 00:36:49.310
(Min Seok Do)

515
00:36:54.280 --> 00:36:55.280
No way.

516
00:36:55.780 --> 00:36:57.550
Kang Jae Gyeong is
just letting this happen?

517
00:36:57.810 --> 00:36:59.540
Letting Chairman Na run
wild when he hasn't even paid...

518
00:36:59.620 --> 00:37:00.970
the balance for the hydrogen technology?

519
00:37:01.050 --> 00:37:02.290
It's so strange. right?

520
00:37:02.520 --> 00:37:04.450
He's someone who deserves
to be thrown out on his ear.

521
00:37:04.720 --> 00:37:05.990
But what's even weirder...

522
00:37:06.590 --> 00:37:08.020
is Kang Jae Gyeong's informant.

523
00:37:08.630 --> 00:37:10.760
You found out? Did he share who it was?

524
00:37:11.590 --> 00:37:13.650
At first. the guy swore he wouldn't talk...

525
00:37:13.730 --> 00:37:16.930
even with a knife to his
throat. He played so hard to get.

526
00:37:17.230 --> 00:37:19.700
But two bottles of whiskey later. he caved.

527
00:37:20.100 --> 00:37:22.030
The guy's a lightweight.

528
00:37:22.110 --> 00:37:23.640
But your brother here has an iron liver.

529
00:37:23.870 --> 00:37:25.730
I don't get drunk. I take after our father.

530
00:37:25.810 --> 00:37:27.440
Anyway. the informant...

531
00:37:28.240 --> 00:37:29.480
Who is the informant?

532
00:37:32.680 --> 00:37:34.080
It was someone we know.

533
00:37:35.590 --> 00:37:37.750
- Na Byeong Mo.
- What?

534
00:37:38.660 --> 00:37:41.360
- Chairman Na?
- That viper...

535
00:37:42.030 --> 00:37:44.330
even offered a
multi-million dollar ad deal...

536
00:37:44.660 --> 00:37:46.900
and said absolutely
not to publish the article.

537
00:37:47.430 --> 00:37:51.100
He said to just send the
tip-off to Kang Jae Gyeong.

538
00:37:53.700 --> 00:37:55.490
So Kang Jae Gyeong is being blackmailed...

539
00:37:55.570 --> 00:37:57.710
by Na Byeong Mo over Dad's murder.

540
00:38:00.640 --> 00:38:02.080
Chairman Na...

541
00:38:04.010 --> 00:38:05.280
likes bonsai trees. right?

542
00:38:09.920 --> 00:38:12.920
This is the bonsai expert. I had
a hard time getting her to come.

543
00:38:15.490 --> 00:38:18.230
If the Chairman finds
out. he'll have our heads.

544
00:38:20.960 --> 00:38:21.970
Hazard pay.

545
00:38:23.630 --> 00:38:26.390
- Wait...
- He won't be back for a while.

546
00:38:26.470 --> 00:38:27.500
Don't worry.

547
00:38:35.250 --> 00:38:37.070
Computer hard drives.
external memory drives. USBs...

548
00:38:37.150 --> 00:38:39.070
Find anything that looks
like a storage device.

549
00:38:39.150 --> 00:38:41.170
Okay. Hospital CCTV footage...

550
00:38:41.250 --> 00:38:43.240
or the connection between Kang
Jae Gyeong and Na Byeong Mo.

551
00:38:43.320 --> 00:38:44.720
I swear. I'll find at least one today.

552
00:38:56.630 --> 00:38:57.630
Seok Do.

553
00:39:00.470 --> 00:39:01.470
Mother.

554
00:39:03.240 --> 00:39:05.710
I hear you haven't been home much lately.

555
00:39:07.440 --> 00:39:09.050
I got a call from Il Jun.

556
00:39:10.280 --> 00:39:11.610
He said there was something he was craving.

557
00:39:13.550 --> 00:39:14.750
Don't do this again.

558
00:39:15.450 --> 00:39:16.620
Or just don't answer his calls.

559
00:39:16.990 --> 00:39:18.490
The kids haven't done anything wrong.

560
00:39:18.660 --> 00:39:21.120
Please leave. I'll give it to them.

561
00:39:23.760 --> 00:39:27.430
You did your best to
save your father-in-law.

562
00:39:28.230 --> 00:39:29.970
I know you were sincere.

563
00:39:32.400 --> 00:39:33.400
I...

564
00:39:35.070 --> 00:39:38.010
just want to know the truth of how he died.

565
00:39:40.010 --> 00:39:42.680
For Il Jun's sake. don't do
anything else you'll regret.

566
00:39:44.350 --> 00:39:45.720
You're a father too.

567
00:39:50.850 --> 00:39:51.890
I guess I'll get what's coming to me.

568
00:40:02.300 --> 00:40:04.420
(Multiful 5. Trace Element Injection)

569
00:40:04.500 --> 00:40:06.200
He quit his job at the hospital.

570
00:40:06.970 --> 00:40:08.610
Why would he be carrying
something like that?

571
00:40:33.600 --> 00:40:36.770
There aren't any golf
courses in that direction.

572
00:40:37.600 --> 00:40:39.100
Kang Jae Gyeong. that crazy girl.

573
00:40:42.440 --> 00:40:44.440
(Additional Agreement on Strategic Investment)

574
00:40:44.540 --> 00:40:47.840
That lunatic. Selling our precious
hydrogen business for this nonsense?

575
00:40:49.050 --> 00:40:50.050
Let's just take it.

576
00:40:55.220 --> 00:40:56.520
You're dead meat. Kang Jae Gyeong.

577
00:40:57.220 --> 00:40:59.480
The Chairman is arriving!

578
00:40:59.560 --> 00:41:00.720
In one minute!

579
00:41:36.660 --> 00:41:38.290
I'm a bit late. Chairman.

580
00:41:39.730 --> 00:41:41.500
Welcome. Team Leader Hwang Jun Hyeon.

581
00:41:42.500 --> 00:41:43.500
Let's go inside.

582
00:41:49.810 --> 00:41:51.870
Well. if it isn't the
traitor of the century.

583
00:41:54.810 --> 00:41:56.880
What are you plotting now. Hwang Jun Hyeon?

584
00:42:00.120 --> 00:42:01.640
I thought you might have lost my card.

585
00:42:01.720 --> 00:42:02.950
so I came to see you in person.

586
00:42:03.420 --> 00:42:06.160
When you said you'd serve
me as your third master.

587
00:42:06.860 --> 00:42:08.730
I didn't realise you were being sincere.

588
00:42:09.130 --> 00:42:11.530
The lifeline I'm clinging to
feels like it's about to snap.

589
00:42:11.960 --> 00:42:13.800
They're trying to hush it up.
but rumours are running rampant.

590
00:42:14.730 --> 00:42:16.670
That Kang Jae Gyeong killed her own father.

591
00:42:18.370 --> 00:42:20.040
How is the company in
more of an uproar now...

592
00:42:20.570 --> 00:42:22.270
than when Father passed away?

593
00:42:22.510 --> 00:42:24.730
But we don't know the truth yet. do we?

594
00:42:24.810 --> 00:42:25.880
True or not.

595
00:42:26.840 --> 00:42:29.810
no soldiers will follow a
general who's lost their trust.

596
00:42:30.250 --> 00:42:32.750
Isn't knowing when to
jump ship a skill in itself?

597
00:42:33.750 --> 00:42:36.410
It looks like you've really
got Kang Jae Gyeong...

598
00:42:36.490 --> 00:42:37.820
by the throat. Chairman Na.

599
00:42:46.800 --> 00:42:47.800
Team Leader Hwang.

600
00:42:49.700 --> 00:42:52.170
Do I look like someone
you can just sound out?

601
00:42:58.170 --> 00:42:59.440
That's what Kang Jae Gyeong said.

602
00:43:00.640 --> 00:43:02.610
That you're the one who killed her father.

603
00:43:03.410 --> 00:43:05.230
She said you're framing her.
but she asked me to help...

604
00:43:05.310 --> 00:43:07.250
since she has no evidence
or way to prove her innocence.

605
00:43:07.950 --> 00:43:09.520
It's not that I believe Kang Jae Gyeong.

606
00:43:10.220 --> 00:43:11.220
but why should I?

607
00:43:22.370 --> 00:43:24.200
After everything it
took for me to get here.

608
00:43:24.800 --> 00:43:27.300
She has to pay the
price for trying to kill me.

609
00:43:29.410 --> 00:43:30.610
Your hit-and-run accident...

610
00:43:31.040 --> 00:43:32.610
Was Kang Jae Gyeong behind that?

611
00:43:33.380 --> 00:43:35.140
She's been trading on her
father's name in all sorts of ways.

612
00:43:35.650 --> 00:43:38.680
So. is there any reason I
should help Kang Jae Gyeong?

613
00:43:40.320 --> 00:43:43.790
The one who ruined a promising
young man's life must be punished.

614
00:43:44.450 --> 00:43:46.360
As an adult. how can I turn a blind eye?

615
00:43:47.520 --> 00:43:49.330
Let him go. and then we'll talk.

616
00:43:49.930 --> 00:43:52.360
About how you plan to get your
revenge on Kang Jae Gyeong.

617
00:43:54.530 --> 00:43:55.530
All right. then.

618
00:44:01.740 --> 00:44:03.770
I'll hand over the
hydrogen technology first.

619
00:44:04.840 --> 00:44:06.810
There's a lot more I
can get besides that...

620
00:44:07.480 --> 00:44:08.540
from Kang Jae Gyeong.

621
00:44:22.430 --> 00:44:23.530
I must say. I'm impressed.

622
00:44:24.330 --> 00:44:25.600
Your judgment and
your ability to act quickly.

623
00:44:26.500 --> 00:44:28.360
Now I see why everyone asks
for you. Team Leader Hwang.

624
00:44:28.930 --> 00:44:29.970
You're too kind.

625
00:44:31.930 --> 00:44:32.940
You should be careful.

626
00:44:35.040 --> 00:44:36.070
Thank you.

627
00:44:40.610 --> 00:44:41.680
Are you hurt?

628
00:44:42.110 --> 00:44:43.710
The pain is mostly gone.

629
00:44:44.550 --> 00:44:46.120
but it flares up whenever
I go down the stairs.

630
00:44:56.060 --> 00:44:57.930
(Hangang University Hospital)

631
00:44:58.230 --> 00:44:59.920
Besides Kang Jae Gyeong.
was there really no one else...

632
00:45:00.000 --> 00:45:01.300
who came to the Chairman's room that day?

633
00:45:01.830 --> 00:45:02.830
No. there wasn't.

634
00:45:03.730 --> 00:45:05.540
After Kang Jae Gyeong left.

635
00:45:05.870 --> 00:45:07.770
it wasn't long before that
happened to the Chairman.

636
00:45:09.370 --> 00:45:10.440
Was there anything out of the ordinary?

637
00:45:12.410 --> 00:45:14.040
Please try to think
carefully one more time.

638
00:45:15.010 --> 00:45:16.780
What was unusual?

639
00:45:19.180 --> 00:45:21.320
Oh. right. The stairs.

640
00:45:22.390 --> 00:45:23.390
The stairs?

641
00:45:23.950 --> 00:45:25.220
It was a bit strange.

642
00:45:26.060 --> 00:45:28.890
The elevator wasn't broken. but
she used the emergency stairs.

643
00:45:30.760 --> 00:45:33.480
(Do Not Enter)

644
00:45:33.560 --> 00:45:34.930
(Stairwell)

645
00:45:36.130 --> 00:45:37.630
She took the stairs on purpose.

646
00:45:38.600 --> 00:45:40.370
So she wouldn't run into Kang Jae Gyeong.

647
00:45:41.140 --> 00:45:42.140
Sorry?

648
00:45:42.710 --> 00:45:45.470
There was someone else there that day.

649
00:46:00.860 --> 00:46:02.160
(VIP Ward)

650
00:46:11.400 --> 00:46:13.460
Surely you don't think...

651
00:46:13.540 --> 00:46:15.240
you got to that chair all by yourself?

652
00:46:22.410 --> 00:46:25.480
It was Na Byeong Mo.
He's trying to frame me for it.

653
00:46:28.520 --> 00:46:30.240
They're trying to hush it up.
but rumours are running rampant.

654
00:46:30.320 --> 00:46:32.020
That Kang Jae Gyeong killed her own father.

655
00:46:32.290 --> 00:46:34.660
But we don't know the truth yet. do we?

656
00:47:01.150 --> 00:47:02.150
(VIP Ward)

657
00:47:39.590 --> 00:47:41.790
Someone with a similar
build to Kang Jae Gyeong...

658
00:47:43.490 --> 00:47:45.830
who can easily get things
in Kang Jae Gyeong's style.

659
00:47:47.760 --> 00:47:50.350
Na Byeong Mo's daughter.
who has a deep-seated...

660
00:47:50.430 --> 00:47:51.900
inferiority complex toward Kang Jae Gyeong.

661
00:47:54.700 --> 00:47:55.710
Na Eun Se.

662
00:47:59.980 --> 00:48:01.010
It was you.

663
00:48:06.980 --> 00:48:08.180
You were the one who killed me.

664
00:48:17.260 --> 00:48:19.780
Come on. you should've
gotten a better place.

665
00:48:19.860 --> 00:48:21.600
I'll give you more money. so let's move.

666
00:48:22.000 --> 00:48:24.300
How can an accomplice to a
slush fund move to a nice place?

667
00:48:25.500 --> 00:48:28.340
Jae Gyeong would have me arrested
the second she finds an excuse.

668
00:48:28.500 --> 00:48:30.860
This place is so tiny. There
isn't even room to hide and cry.

669
00:48:30.940 --> 00:48:32.240
How can you live here?

670
00:48:36.250 --> 00:48:37.510
I know you've always found...

671
00:48:39.050 --> 00:48:41.420
a secluded corner to swallow your tears...

672
00:48:42.250 --> 00:48:45.150
like the kitchen. the wine
cellar. and the garage.

673
00:48:45.720 --> 00:48:47.560
Kang Jae Gyeong really tormented you.

674
00:48:47.860 --> 00:48:49.190
You played a part in it too. you know.

675
00:48:52.190 --> 00:48:53.200
I'm sorry.

676
00:48:54.700 --> 00:48:56.030
I wasn't a good person.

677
00:48:56.830 --> 00:48:58.470
I can't believe how immature I was.

678
00:49:02.440 --> 00:49:04.470
Listen to you. acting like
you're all grown up now.

679
00:49:06.680 --> 00:49:09.880
I may be immature. but I'm handy.

680
00:49:12.310 --> 00:49:14.350
See? When I say I'll do something. I do it.

681
00:49:16.520 --> 00:49:18.070
If we leak this. don't you think we can...

682
00:49:18.150 --> 00:49:19.790
keep the hydrogen business from Taeha?

683
00:49:20.060 --> 00:49:22.120
Taeha is the one at a
disadvantage in this secret contract.

684
00:49:22.490 --> 00:49:24.310
Na Byeong Mo won't even bat an eye.

685
00:49:24.390 --> 00:49:26.630
Only Choiseong will be
shaken by the contract scandal.

686
00:49:27.060 --> 00:49:29.230
- But still...
- Jae Seong's right.

687
00:49:29.570 --> 00:49:32.640
And this isn't even proof that
Jae Gyeong is the real culprit.

688
00:49:33.540 --> 00:49:37.640
- Any luck finding that informant?
- Well. about that...

689
00:49:39.240 --> 00:49:40.700
- Darn it.
- My role here...

690
00:49:40.780 --> 00:49:42.000
is to be malnourished. Mom.

691
00:49:42.080 --> 00:49:45.210
- I've got no strength in my hands.
- You really should be more careful.

692
00:49:45.480 --> 00:49:47.620
Let me see if I have some
pants you can change into.

693
00:49:48.650 --> 00:49:49.750
What are you doing?

694
00:49:49.850 --> 00:49:52.420
Don't say anything to
Mom until we know for sure.

695
00:49:53.860 --> 00:49:55.220
What do you take your brother for?

696
00:49:55.460 --> 00:49:56.880
I was going to make something up anyway.

697
00:49:56.960 --> 00:49:58.150
As if.

698
00:49:58.230 --> 00:50:00.980
- You were itching to say something.
- Hide!

699
00:50:01.060 --> 00:50:02.500
- You're just embarrassed.
- I said. hide!

700
00:50:02.600 --> 00:50:04.270
What now?

701
00:50:07.040 --> 00:50:08.670
- What?
- Kang Jae Gyeong's lackey.

702
00:50:18.680 --> 00:50:20.150
That punk.

703
00:50:20.480 --> 00:50:23.150
Where have you been
wandering? You're finally crawling in.

704
00:50:23.520 --> 00:50:25.150
Who did you betray this time?

705
00:50:25.920 --> 00:50:28.740
He must have conspired with Kang
Jae Gyeong to get to Chairman Na.

706
00:50:28.820 --> 00:50:29.880
"Betrayal" is a bit much.

707
00:50:29.960 --> 00:50:31.480
Hey. the first betrayal is the hardest.

708
00:50:31.560 --> 00:50:33.430
The next ones are a
piece of cake. you know?

709
00:50:33.630 --> 00:50:35.730
- Speaking from experience?
- That's it. Why you little...

710
00:50:39.000 --> 00:50:41.440
- Are you okay?
- Gosh. baggy pants.

711
00:50:41.740 --> 00:50:43.540
Totally my style. I love them.

712
00:50:45.170 --> 00:50:46.560
Do you want to bet if Hwang Jun Hyeon...

713
00:50:46.640 --> 00:50:48.300
has switched to Taeha's side?

714
00:50:48.380 --> 00:50:49.410
We'll see who's right.

715
00:50:49.650 --> 00:50:52.050
Why would you make such a childish bet?

716
00:50:54.250 --> 00:50:55.780
We can just find out for ourselves.

717
00:51:04.690 --> 00:51:06.000
You're having bread in
the middle of the night?

718
00:51:06.400 --> 00:51:09.870
Bang Geul just dropped it
off. Do you want to try some?

719
00:51:10.170 --> 00:51:11.170
She was here?

720
00:51:11.400 --> 00:51:12.430
Yes.

721
00:51:27.050 --> 00:51:29.080
(History. No Connected Devices)

722
00:51:30.520 --> 00:51:32.690
Please insert the memory card.

723
00:51:35.590 --> 00:51:37.690
That meticulous jerk.

724
00:51:38.990 --> 00:51:40.000
Grandma.

725
00:51:41.300 --> 00:51:43.630
What do you think?
It's nice and fluffy. right?

726
00:51:44.600 --> 00:51:45.770
I haven't eaten it yet.

727
00:51:46.600 --> 00:51:48.600
It's more delicious with milk.

728
00:51:54.980 --> 00:51:55.980
It is tasty.

729
00:51:56.850 --> 00:51:58.830
Oh. right. Today's trash day.

730
00:51:58.910 --> 00:52:02.150
Oh. I'll take it out. Taking
out the trash is my hobby.

731
00:52:09.630 --> 00:52:10.630
(Unannounced Fire Inspection)

732
00:52:12.560 --> 00:52:14.400
That calculating jerk.

733
00:52:16.230 --> 00:52:18.900
Oh. my. You scared me.

734
00:52:20.100 --> 00:52:22.020
You scared me. Mom.

735
00:52:22.100 --> 00:52:24.070
Aren't you going to make use of me?

736
00:52:28.680 --> 00:52:30.250
What is it now?

737
00:52:30.480 --> 00:52:33.650
I made some savoury pancakes. I
brought them for you. Mr. Hwang.

738
00:52:33.880 --> 00:52:35.070
I don't want any.

739
00:52:35.150 --> 00:52:38.690
How can you say no when
it smells this delicious?

740
00:52:38.920 --> 00:52:41.520
- Come on out.
- Oh. honestly.

741
00:52:41.690 --> 00:52:44.190
You need to eat. You must
be getting hungry by now.

742
00:52:44.660 --> 00:52:47.030
They turned out so delicious.

743
00:52:50.170 --> 00:52:51.170
Right?

744
00:52:55.000 --> 00:52:56.170
(Recycle Bin)

745
00:52:57.040 --> 00:52:58.070
Should I make some more?

746
00:52:58.640 --> 00:53:00.630
- No. that's fine. I'll have that.
- Seriously.

747
00:53:00.710 --> 00:53:03.730
No. Goodness me. Here. have this one too.

748
00:53:03.810 --> 00:53:05.400
- Okay.
- Have this and then eat some more.

749
00:53:05.480 --> 00:53:06.580
I'll take it inside.

750
00:53:06.850 --> 00:53:09.280
Come over here. It won't take long.

751
00:53:09.550 --> 00:53:12.980
- Grandma. I'm back with groceries.
- You've gone to so much trouble.

752
00:53:13.060 --> 00:53:14.990
- Sure.
- Jun Hyeon. give her a hand.

753
00:53:16.430 --> 00:53:17.760
Thank you.

754
00:53:18.930 --> 00:53:20.000
Come in.

755
00:53:33.980 --> 00:53:36.380
Oh. I was just taking a selfie.

756
00:53:38.150 --> 00:53:40.050
Just one quick selfie.

757
00:54:11.010 --> 00:54:13.770
First. replace the laptops
for the Chemical DX Team...

758
00:54:13.850 --> 00:54:15.750
then move on to the
Talent Acquisition Team.

759
00:54:16.020 --> 00:54:17.510
There are departmental
meetings this afternoon.

760
00:54:17.590 --> 00:54:18.620
so provide support for those.

761
00:54:27.400 --> 00:54:28.400
Hey.

762
00:54:29.570 --> 00:54:30.600
What's wrong with you two today?

763
00:54:32.940 --> 00:54:35.460
It seems like Hwang Jun
Hyeon is plotting something.

764
00:54:35.540 --> 00:54:37.210
but we have no way of knowing what it is.

765
00:54:38.040 --> 00:54:40.930
I can't take it anymore. I'm
going to be a man and just...

766
00:54:41.010 --> 00:54:43.800
- No.
- Is this the resignation letter?

767
00:54:43.880 --> 00:54:46.350
Is that the resignation letter
Hwang Jun Hyeon is dying to see?

768
00:54:48.080 --> 00:54:51.270
"To Jun Hyeon. Heart. Hello.
The first time I saw you..."

769
00:54:51.350 --> 00:54:55.280
"They were the things I wouldn't
have done before I met you..."

770
00:54:55.360 --> 00:54:57.390
This letter is meant to
be touching. you know?

771
00:54:58.060 --> 00:54:59.660
I rewrote it more than ten times.

772
00:55:01.730 --> 00:55:04.020
After all we've been through together.

773
00:55:04.100 --> 00:55:06.000
I doubt he's feeling
great about this either.

774
00:55:06.400 --> 00:55:08.870
Jun Hyeon isn't that bad of a guy.

775
00:55:09.910 --> 00:55:14.810
No. he's totally cold-blooded.
He's harsh and just ice-cold.

776
00:55:16.710 --> 00:55:19.210
He's kind of like my dad.

777
00:55:21.550 --> 00:55:22.580
Bang Geul.

778
00:55:23.250 --> 00:55:25.990
The Chairman cared for you a lot.

779
00:55:26.960 --> 00:55:28.190
He just wasn't good at showing it.

780
00:55:28.560 --> 00:55:31.230
It's okay. I don't resent
my dad. He was busy.

781
00:55:31.630 --> 00:55:32.630
That's not true.

782
00:55:33.000 --> 00:55:35.930
When he heard that you
were being bullied in the US.

783
00:55:36.300 --> 00:55:39.150
the Chairman skipped the opening
of the Daesan Hydrogen Complex...

784
00:55:39.230 --> 00:55:40.690
which he'd been looking
forward to for years...

785
00:55:40.770 --> 00:55:43.330
- and flew straight to the US.
- The Chairman did?

786
00:55:43.410 --> 00:55:44.440
Of course.

787
00:55:45.370 --> 00:55:48.010
He tore into them until
they were a crying mess.

788
00:55:48.340 --> 00:55:50.100
He even got a written promise from them...

789
00:55:50.180 --> 00:55:51.550
that they would never bully you again.

790
00:55:51.780 --> 00:55:54.850
But even after that.
he was still so furious.

791
00:55:56.650 --> 00:55:59.290
So that's why their
attitudes suddenly changed.

792
00:56:01.820 --> 00:56:04.460
But why did he leave without seeing
me? He went all the way to the US.

793
00:56:04.730 --> 00:56:06.900
Because if he saw you.
his heart would soften.

794
00:56:07.660 --> 00:56:09.600
and he wouldn't have
been able to leave you there.

795
00:56:10.170 --> 00:56:11.300
But if he brought you back.

796
00:56:11.800 --> 00:56:13.440
you would have had to
deal with Jae Gyeong again.

797
00:56:14.270 --> 00:56:15.570
That's why he held back.

798
00:56:16.000 --> 00:56:18.010
He knew everything she was doing?

799
00:56:19.240 --> 00:56:22.040
The Chairman always felt sorry
that he couldn't do more for you.

800
00:56:23.080 --> 00:56:25.250
He thought that was
how he could protect you.

801
00:56:25.650 --> 00:56:27.280
It wasn't because he didn't love you.

802
00:56:27.850 --> 00:56:30.220
If he was going to die like this anyway.

803
00:56:31.450 --> 00:56:34.460
why did he hide his feelings?
Why didn't he say anything?

804
00:56:36.460 --> 00:56:37.830
He always seemed so larger-than-life.

805
00:56:39.700 --> 00:56:41.760
But the Chairman was
just a father. after all.

806
00:56:41.930 --> 00:56:43.670
Why are you crying now too?

807
00:56:44.570 --> 00:56:47.340
Goodness. Coffee's on me.

808
00:56:47.640 --> 00:56:50.030
- An iced vanilla latte. right?
- An iced vanilla latte.

809
00:56:50.110 --> 00:56:51.110
Just rest here.

810
00:56:51.510 --> 00:56:53.580
Get it from the place
right in front of the office.

811
00:56:54.510 --> 00:56:56.550
Ask them for two pumps of syrup.

812
00:57:03.290 --> 00:57:05.570
- Mom.
- Bang Geul's mom.

813
00:57:05.650 --> 00:57:06.780
If you're done with the bean sprouts.

814
00:57:06.860 --> 00:57:08.040
bring them here so I can blanch.

815
00:57:08.120 --> 00:57:09.390
Yes. coming.

816
00:57:10.660 --> 00:57:13.130
Hwang Jun Hyeon is going
on a business trip today.

817
00:57:13.700 --> 00:57:15.460
A business trip? Where to?

818
00:57:18.100 --> 00:57:20.270
Grandma forgot.

819
00:57:21.040 --> 00:57:22.970
She said it started with Dae-something.

820
00:57:23.640 --> 00:57:25.070
Dae?

821
00:57:25.970 --> 00:57:28.640
Could it be Daesan? You mean
the Daesan Hydrogen Complex?

822
00:57:32.110 --> 00:57:34.150
I told you. you didn't
have to come all this way.

823
00:57:35.580 --> 00:57:37.220
The Chairman doesn't like variables.

824
00:57:37.490 --> 00:57:39.890
Secretary Jo. are you sure
you're not just acting on your own?

825
00:57:43.830 --> 00:57:45.530
Can you really get it out
without the staff knowing?

826
00:57:45.760 --> 00:57:48.700
After I disable the CCTVs.
I'll set off the fire alarm.

827
00:57:49.300 --> 00:57:50.920
The fire trucks will take
five minutes to arrive.

828
00:57:51.000 --> 00:57:52.970
I'll get it out then. so just wait.

829
00:57:53.740 --> 00:57:54.800
Don't worry.

830
00:57:55.740 --> 00:57:57.140
If you're that suspicious.

831
00:57:57.810 --> 00:57:59.010
you can come with me.

832
00:58:14.760 --> 00:58:16.710
- Let's go.
- Fire. There's a fire!

833
00:58:16.790 --> 00:58:18.850
- Evacuate.
- Evacuate.

834
00:58:18.930 --> 00:58:19.930
Fire!

835
00:58:37.380 --> 00:58:38.380
(Enter Password)

836
00:58:43.620 --> 00:58:44.720
(Transferring File)

837
00:58:50.830 --> 00:58:51.860
Why is it doing this again?

838
00:58:52.690 --> 00:58:53.860
But he's dead.

839
00:59:03.410 --> 00:59:06.010
(Lee Sang Jae)

840
00:59:07.340 --> 00:59:11.150
- I'll call you back when...
- Bang Geul is there.

841
00:59:13.480 --> 00:59:17.050
- What?
- Manager Park said Ms. Jo told her.

842
00:59:17.320 --> 00:59:19.820
She seems to know that
you and Taeha made contact.

843
00:59:20.360 --> 00:59:21.960
I think Bang Geul figured something out.

844
00:59:23.230 --> 00:59:24.230
What do you mean?

845
00:59:27.230 --> 00:59:28.460
What are you doing?

846
00:59:30.000 --> 00:59:32.130
- Kang Bang Geul!
- You...

847
00:59:33.870 --> 00:59:35.970
Did you really betray Kang Jae Gyeong?

848
00:59:37.410 --> 00:59:39.010
Did you side with Taeha?

849
00:59:39.440 --> 00:59:41.510
I told you to lay low.

850
00:59:42.140 --> 00:59:43.280
What are you doing here?

851
00:59:51.690 --> 00:59:53.990
What are you doing? Are you crazy?

852
00:59:54.990 --> 00:59:56.760
The rule is to get rid of any witnesses.

853
00:59:57.660 --> 00:59:58.660
Young Lady.

854
00:59:59.800 --> 01:00:02.960
- Wake up. Are you okay?
- Hey. Jun Hyeon.

855
01:00:10.740 --> 01:00:13.880
Darn it. Jun Hyeon. Wait.

856
01:00:14.340 --> 01:00:16.310
Young Lady. are you all right?

857
01:00:16.610 --> 01:00:17.680
Mr. Park.

858
01:00:18.210 --> 01:00:19.850
I'm okay.

859
01:00:31.030 --> 01:00:32.210
- Bang Geul.
- Goodness.

860
01:00:32.290 --> 01:00:33.300
Bang Geul!

861
01:00:36.200 --> 01:00:38.200
Yes. we're at the Daesan Hydrogen Complex.

862
01:00:38.970 --> 01:00:40.470
You should've just gone to the US!

863
01:00:40.800 --> 01:00:42.600
You said you wanted to run
away. so why are you still here?

864
01:00:43.210 --> 01:00:45.470
Why did I never once truly
appreciate this wonderful girl?

865
01:00:46.170 --> 01:00:48.240
The one who would just smile so
brightly when I pushed her away.

866
01:00:49.810 --> 01:00:51.780
Wake up. Bang Geul!

867
01:00:52.180 --> 01:00:54.480
Open your eyes! Can't you hear your dad?

868
01:01:43.430 --> 01:01:44.930
You're still here?

869
01:01:46.370 --> 01:01:47.370
Jae Seong.

870
01:02:05.590 --> 01:02:07.090
This is your last chance.

871
01:02:08.120 --> 01:02:10.230
Make sure my father wakes
up. Your life depends on it.

872
01:02:11.430 --> 01:02:12.430
Yes. sir.

873
01:02:23.410 --> 01:02:24.410
Father.

874
01:02:25.140 --> 01:02:26.140
Hang on...

875
01:02:27.340 --> 01:02:29.040
just a little longer.

876
01:02:35.380 --> 01:02:36.690
Help me!

877
01:02:46.830 --> 01:02:47.960
Is anyone there?

878
01:02:48.460 --> 01:02:51.770
I'm trapped in here. Is anyone there?

879
01:02:52.830 --> 01:02:54.640
I'm trapped in here!

880
01:02:55.200 --> 01:02:56.910
I'm Hwang Jun Hyeon!

881
01:03:08.780 --> 01:03:11.750
(Reborn Rookie)

882
01:03:32.910 --> 01:03:34.530
{\an8}I'm letting you in on my revenge.

883
01:03:34.610 --> 01:03:36.180
{\an8}So from now on. we do everything together.

884
01:03:36.410 --> 01:03:38.400
{\an8}I found the original CCTV
footage from the hospital.

885
01:03:38.480 --> 01:03:41.950
{\an8}Let's show the world what
kind of man Na Byeong Mo is.

886
01:03:42.050 --> 01:03:43.210
{\an8}We've secured circumstantial evidence...

887
01:03:43.290 --> 01:03:44.290
{\an8}pointing to the real culprit.

888
01:03:44.820 --> 01:03:46.680
{\an8}Get all our connections in
the prosecution and the police.

889
01:03:46.760 --> 01:03:48.780
{\an8}If you don't want to be on
the news with Na Byeong Mo.

890
01:03:48.860 --> 01:03:51.190
{\an8}- then throw him in jail now.
- So you're looking for a fight?

891
01:03:51.990 --> 01:03:53.630
{\an8}Do you think my father will
let you get away with this?

892
01:03:54.230 --> 01:03:56.930
{\an8}Get rid of him. And make
sure there's nothing left.

893
01:03:57.270 --> 01:04:00.290
{\an8}You're really something else.
ordering someone to be killed.

894
01:04:00.370 --> 01:04:02.420
{\an8}How about we take over all of Taeha?

895
01:04:02.500 --> 01:04:04.930
{\an8}In that case. may I tell you what I want?

896
01:04:05.010 --> 01:04:07.710
{\an8}My final target is
Chairwoman Kang Jae Gyeong.

897
01:04:08.305 --> 01:05:08.809
